// Changeling = a CDA ([CR#702.73a,604.3]): "this object is every creature
// type", functioning everywhere. Name-carrying: the every-creature-type
// modification (an open-set subtype fill, not a Set/Add list) doesn't
// exist in the Modification grammar yet — the body arrives with it.
KeywordAbility(
    name: "Changeling",
    template: "changeling",
    abilities: [],
)
